    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?verb ?lemma WHERE {
  ?verb wdt:P31 wd:Q24905;   # Instance of a verb
        wdt:P407 wd:Q256;    # Language of work or name is Turkish

  FILTER (lang(?lemma) = 'en') 
}

question.string: has life expectancy in iran grown in any year after 1999?

query.sparql:
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
    PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
    PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
    PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> 
    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> 
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q794 p:P2250 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P2250 ?lifeExpectancy .
  ?statement pq:P585 ?date .
  FILTER(YEAR(?date) > 1999) .
  FILTER EXISTS {
    ?previousStatement p:P2250 ?prevStatement .
    ?prevStatement ps:P2250 ?previousLifeExpectancy .
    ?prevStatement pq:P585 ?prevDate .
    FILTER(YEAR(?prevDate) < YEAR(?date) && ?previousLifeExpectancy < ?lifeExpectancy)
  }
}

    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?player ?playerLabel (MAX(?goals) AS ?maxGoals) WHERE {
  ?player wdt:P106 wd:Q937857;  # Profession: football player
          wdt:P54 ?club.
  ?club pq:P1351 ?goals.  #points/goals scored property

}
GROUP BY ?player ?playerLabel
ORDER BY DESC(?maxGoals)
LIMIT 1

question.string: which river is longer, the Seine or Elbe？

    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
